title: Essentials of Oceanography, 6th ed - Garrison - [Non-Fiction] PD
description:
| ISBN-10: 0840061552 | 436 pages | PDF | 82 MB

The sixth edition of "Essentials of Oceanography, International Edition" conveys Garrison's enthusiasm for oceanography to non-science students taking an introductory course. It is a streamlined version of his bestselling "Oceanography, International Edition" text, but was created specifically to meet the needs of a shorter course. This text provides a basic understanding of the scientific questions, complexities, and uncertainties involved in ocean use, and the role and importance of oceans in nurturing and sustaining life on the planet.
